data.description: Enjoy the beautiful sunrises and sunsets right off your deck. This home is a fantastic 4 bedroom 2 bath home. Fantastic kitchen with rustic hickory cabinets, granite tops and stainless steel appliances. Stone Fireplace in the living room with  bay window seating to snuggle into in front of he fire and kick back and relax. This home has a detached 30x50 insulated and heated garage, all concrete driveway with an additional parking pad, its own private boat ramp. Great home for entertaining.
